data.description: Have you ever wondered what it would be like to live in the very heart of St Augustine? Here's your chance! In 2022, the original house at this location was completely removed and this 3 bedroom, 2 bath 1392sq ft gem was built from the ground up that now meets all the latest in structural codes with hip, fresh styling! Charming, inviting, completely up to date with a modern floor plan, hurricane rated impact windows, LVP floors throughout, brand new HVAC, brand new plumbing, brand new wiring and electrical service, brand new septic, brand new appliances, and architectural shingle roof- this home offers far more than any typical renovation. The footprint was even moved back 10 feet to better center it in the middle of the lot! Where else could you find the charm of living along the historic "Scenic A1A” and also have the confidence of a brand-new build that offers the latest in security and style! From the front door you'll see the entrance to one of the Florida’s elite music venues- St Augustine Amphitheatre, as well as St Augustine Lighthouse, and directly across the street is Anastasia State Park! Whether you're a music aficionado, a Wildlife lover, adventurer in the Great Outdoors, visiting Historic Downtown or our world-class beaches, you are a short hop to the BEST of all that St Augustine offers!  Located on a short stretch of "county zoning", flood zone "X", this home has the lowest property and utility costs while having unmatched proximity to the best of everything. Many properties claim to offer a limited version of what this house truly provides! Come and see for yourself what a rare find this home is and take advantage of this once in a lifetime value while you can!
